Larrimac Table Tennis Club is located on a 100 year old golf course and in the winter Table Tennis is peing played. 
The club includes 4 professional tables, a Robopong to practice, paddle and balls are available. 
Any type of players of all ages are welcome. 
The club is located In Chelsea, Quebec at 1148 Route 105, about 15 minutes from Ottawa. 
The is open on Wednesday from 5:30pm to 10:00pm and Sunday from 2:30pm to 5:30pm.
We also have a Bar with bartender for various type of alcohalic and non-alcoholic beverages.
Come and Join us and have some fun...See you there...
